Subject: [PATCH v7 1/3] tty: rename tty_kopen() and add new function tty_kopen_shared()
Date:   Tue,  7 Jul 2020 18:59:56 +0200
Message-Id: <20200707165958.16522-2-u.kleine-koenig@pengutronix.de>
